Setup
=====

```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Usage
=====


1. Run the code mod on what you want.
```
# bowler run <mod_script> <path_to_directory_or_file_to_modify>
# For example
bowler run foreignkey_on_delete_mod.py ~/src/edx-platform

# to update the User.is_authenticated and User.is_anonymous as properties
bowler run auth_anonymous_update.py ~/src/edx-platform
```

```
# PROMPT HELP
"y": "apply this hunk",
"n": "skip this hunk",
"a": "apply this hunk and all remaining hunks for this file",
"d": "skip this hunk and all remaining hunks for this file",
"q": "quit; do not apply this hunk or any remaining hunks",
"?": "show help",
```

2. Correct any formatting to match your formatting rules.
